    dc:title "Systematics and convergent evolution in three Australian genera of Pepsinae spider wasps (Hymenoptera: Pompilidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4627887>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4627875>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4627877>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4627881>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4627883> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4627887>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Australian female Ctenocerini sensu Evans (1972) other than the genera treated here. (a) Apical metasomal segments of a paratype of Cteniziphontes protervus (Turner, 1915) (NHML), lateral view; (b) head of the holotype of Apoclavelia aganippeae Evans, 1972 (ANIC), anterior view; and (c) head of the holotype of Austroclavelia venator Evans, 1972 (ANIC), anterior view. Scale bars: 1 mm. ((a) lacks a scale bar; no measurement data available due to lack of access to the paratype.)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4627887/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4627875>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Maurillus argenticapitis, sp. nov., holotype female.(a) Head, anterior view; (b) head and anterior part of antenna, ventrolateral view; (c) head and mesosoma, lateral view; (d) head and anterior part of mesosoma, dorsal view; (e) posterior part of mesosoma and metasoma, dorsal view; (f) fore wing and anterior part of hind wing; (g) head and mesosoma, dorsal view; (h) apical part of fore tibia, dorsal view; (i) right fore tarsus, dorsal view; and (j) right hind pretarsus, dorsal view. Scale bars: 0.1 mm for (j), 0.5 mm for (h) and (i) and 1 mm for others." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4627875/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4627877>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Maurillus australis Smith, holotype female. (a) Head, anterior view; (b) clypeus and mandible, anterior view; (c) head and anterior part of mesosoma, lateral view; (d) scape, dorsal (above) and lateral view (below); (e) head and anterior part of pronotum, dorsal view; (f) posterior part of propodeum and metasoma, dorsal view; (g) fore and hind wings; (h) posterior part of mesosoma and anterior part of metasoma, dorsolateral view; (i) apical part of right fore tibia, medial view; and (j) hind tibia, dorsal view. Scale bars: 1 mm. ((d), (i) and (j) lack scale bars (no measurement data available due to lack of access to the holotype).)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4627877/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4627881>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Maurilloides nigrisoma, sp. nov., holotype female.(a) Head, anterior view; (b) head and anterior part of mesosoma, dorsal view; (c) head and anterior part of mesosoma, dorsolateral view; (d) scape, dorsal view; (e) head and mesosoma, lateral view; (f) left hind pretarsus, lateral view; (g) metapostnotum and propodeum, posterodorsal view; (h) fore wing; (i) posterior part of mesosoma and metasoma, dorsal view; and (j) posterior part of propodeum and metasoma, lateral view. Scale bars: 0.1 mm for (f) and 1 mm for others." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4627881/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4627883>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Evansiclavelia poecilopteryx, sp. nov., holotype female. (a) Head, anterior view (arrow, frontal bridge); (b) head and anterior part of mesosoma, dorsal view; (c) head and mesosoma, lateral view; (d) head and mesosoma,dorsolateral view (arrow,occipital suture); (e) posterior part of mesosoma, dorsolateral view; (f) apical part of right fore tibia, medial view (arrow, apicomedial spine); (g) apical part of left fore tibia, lateral view (arrow, apicolateral spine); (h) body, legs and wings, lateral view; (i) body, part of legs and wings, dorsal view; (j) fore and hind wings; and (k) head, anteroventral view. Scale bars: 0.1 mm for (f) and (g) and 1 mm for others." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4627883/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

